content:
Increase Customer Engagement by Using Marketing Cloud Engagement for Insurance.

Send Customized Emails to Insurance Customers Using Marketing Cloud. Create and send emails using Marketing Cloud Engagement for Insurance Cloud. Email templates help insurance providers set up product-related emails and provide a head start on implementing Marketing Cloud campaigns.

Remind Policyholders About Renewals With Marketing Journeys. Use a prebuilt insurance policy renewal journey to send emails to policyholders when their policies are due for renewal in less than 30 days.

Discover Marketing Cloud Data Extension Templates in Insurance. Use prebuilt data extension templates for Marketing Cloud assets in insurance.
title: Enhance Customer Engagement with Salesforce Marketing Cloud for Insurance
